track_notes:
Bit of a slog uphill all the way takes 1 hr 30 mins from start to summit 1 hour 20 mins on the downhill back to your car.

Pretty Easy track, park at first gate turn left down Solus Rd, when you come to second gate turn right uphill to Summit. Watch for the last turn up to summit, very red track and you may see antennas at top at that stage.
